cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the problem of label shift in modern neural networks and proposes a calibration approach to improve domain adaptation. The paper focuses on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI) and specifically deals with image classification tasks (cs.CV). The paper also mentions medical diagnosis, which falls under the category of natural language processing and computational biology (cs.CL) and discusses the issue of bias, which is relevant to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
